    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessemus nos domnus
                            <rs key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/2004" key="#Marquis/duke">Romovald</persName> summus
                            <rs key="#Marquis/duke">dux</rs> genti Langobardorum tibi <persName
                            ref="#people/3453" key="#Abbots">Zacharia</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabili</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbati</rs> omnem portionem substantia quod <name
                            ref="Toto Transpadanus">Totuni Transpadano</name>, hoc est <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                                ><rs key="#Houses">casas</rs>, <rs key="#Wine">vineas</rs>, <rs
                                key="#Landed_possessions">territoria</rs>, cultum et incultum,
                            movilia atque inmovilia, omnia et in omnibus de quicquid nominati Totuni
                            pertenuit portionem</rs> et quod post suum reliquid discessum tibi
                        [i][********] Zacharię venerabili abbati concessemus possedendum, qui ipse
                        Toto habetare videbatur sub <placeName ref="#places/3420"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property">Sancto
                            Valentino</placeName> quatenus ab hodierna die habeas et possedeas ipsa
                        substantia tu qui super Zacharia venerabili abbate quocumque exinde facere
                        volueris in tua sit potestatem et a nullum quempiam hominem nulla habeas
                        aliquando aliqua questionem aut reprehensione, sed perpetuis temporibus per
                        hunc nostrum firmissimum preceptum securiter et firmiter ipsa iam nominata
                        substantia habere et possedere valeas. Quod vero <rs
                            key="#Marquis’/ducal/princely_diploma">preceptum concessionis</rs> ex
                        iussione nominate potestati dictavi ego <persName
                            key="#Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/3454">Persus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">vicedominus et referendario</rs> tibi
                            <persName ref="#people/3455" key="#Notary">Grausoni</persName> notario
                        scribendum. Actum <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/110"
                            >Benevento</placeName> in <rs key="#Palatium">palatio</rs> mense aprile
                        per indictione sexta. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
